from the system in ther terminal, you can use the Django shell to delete a user. Here's how you can do it:

1. Open your terminal and navigate to your Django project directory.
2. Run the Django shell with the following command: 
python manage.py shell
3. In the shell, you can import the User model and delete a user by their username

